也大幅增长，具体原因是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "除了美元，对欧元，英镑，日元，韩元，新台币，越南盾都在上涨。 人民币指数已经涨一年了。 不是说升值会击垮出口吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4f3c9fbb5d50657e6181fd911993c76c.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "117 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2046773452716217677"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkMGJ9cvl+4lwEAMaCTExOTg0NzQwNCCywJHRBjAAOLEBQAtyEzIwNDY3NzM0NTI3MTYyMTc2Nzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1780934003.312021", "card_id": "Q_2047254423580012881", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2026 各地高考历史题，难度怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4dcbab35f16f9b5a87e456ffbaf8ec8c.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2047254423580012881"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkMGJ9cvl+4lwEAMaCTExOTg2NDEzMSCiwJjRBjAAOElADHITMjA0NzI1NDQyMzU4MDAxMjg4MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1780934003.312444", "card_id": "Q_2046903500739700675", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "住房公积金管理条例修订征求意见，新增装修、物业费等用途，并允许灵活就业人员自愿缴存，如何解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "6 月 5 日，住建部发布关于《住房公积金管理条例（修订征求意见稿）》公开征求意见的通知，对于公积金管理制度提出多项改革措施。 条例第二十四条将住房公积金提取情形由 6 种拓展至 9 种，包括支付房租；购买、建造、翻建、大修自住住房；偿还购房贷款本息；装修自住住房不超过一定额度；支付自住住房物业费；离休、退休；完全丧失劳动能力，并与单位终止劳动（人事）关系；出境定居以及经国务院批准的其他住房消费情形。 其中，新增的 3 种情形分别为装修自住住房不超过一定额度、支付自住住房物业费和经国务院批准的其他住房消费情形。 此外，条例明确原条例规定单位以外的其他单位及其在职职工，可参照条例规定执行；个体工商户、非全日制从业人员以及其他灵活就业人员，可自愿参加住房公积金制度。 根据《全国住房公积金 2024 年年度报告》，截至 2024 年末，全国住房公积金累计缴存总额 32.79 万亿元，缴存余额 10.93 万亿元。住房公积金管理条例修订征求意见 拟全周期支持住房消费"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-20814908e3a6c6882b077648ee837957.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "97 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2046903500739700675"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkMGJ9cvl+4lwEAMaCTExOTg1MDg0MCDQspPRBjAAOFhADXITMjA0NjkwMzUwMDczOTcwMDY3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1780934003.313169", "card_id": "Q_2047333025197904792", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待乌贼、肘子、天下霸唱、猫腻等网络作家发起的反抄袭倡议书? 网文的抄袭到底该如何整治？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "前段时间，我会修空调单章控诉三九音域抄袭，三九称自己是致敬，这个争议事件看似平息了 但是 6 月 8 日，乌贼，肘子，血红，天下霸唱，猫腻，我会修空调，以及晋江，刺猬猫，番茄的几百位作家，都在这个反抄袭倡议书上签名了，到底怎样整治网文的抄袭?"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ae010797e4d231a6940a0349fedc3760_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2047333025197904792"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkMGJ9cvl+4lwEAMaCTExOTg3MDE4OSDW0pnRBjAAODhADnITMjA0NzMzMzAyNTE5NzkwNDc5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1780934003.313612", "car